{"tid":743250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺「五毛分化」已經變咗一個thought-terminating cliche","createTime":"2018-07-15T09:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T07:58:41.000Z","uid":51129,"like":14,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d7982eefdbb1b1ef1ed654311aed58e14540d95f","tid":743250,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T09:11:20.000Z","msg":"由知道五毛會吹風，變到一有任何輿論風向就立即認定一定係五毛所為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n任何議題事無大小，總之唔啱我心水嘅立場trend咗就一定係五毛攪事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌醫學霸權就一定係五毛想引入大陸醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n維護書面語就係五毛想扼殺粵語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而反對書面語就係五毛特登將議題由反蝗語spin去反書面語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鍾意討論風化、軼事多過正經新聞嘅全部係五毛有心分化港人關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f271cd16f43af4875813f5c53cc89e9291ef23","tid":743250,"uid":47359,"like":17,"dislike":11,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/171444_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F171444_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=43b9a6be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/171446_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F171446_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=48e781bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/171448_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.p